cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with adversarial attacks on images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the limitations of existing methods and proposes a new approach, which falls under the category of algorithmic techniques (cs.AI) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper uses probabilistic methods and certificates, which are related to neural networks (cs.NE).
